## Phase 3: ImageFS & Proton Assets from Pipetto APK
- The Pipetto repo does NOT include imagefs in assets (it's downloaded separately)
- Our project already has [imagefs.txz](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/assets/imagefs.txz) bundled
- Keep our imagefs approach but verify compatibility

